# This repository keeps its package source in ./openwrt-squid-profile-ui.
# For direct SDK builds, use the documented Docker workflow, which copies that
# directory to package/feeds/custom/luci-app-squid-profiles.
#
# To publish a conventional OpenWrt feed, mirror the package directory to a
# feed repository root as ./luci-app-squid-profiles, then add that feed:
#
# src-git squid_profiles https://github.com/heralight/openwrt-squid-profile-feed.git
